summary: Meet the Cool Duck - The Cool Duck is the ultimate symbol of coolness, charm, and fun. It embodies the spirit of creating a lively and engaging community where everyone can share in the fun. The Cool Duck leads a community that values fun, camaraderie, and splashy adventures. Participants can earn exclusive rewards and perks by being active in the community and are encouraged to spread the joy of $QUACK by inviting friends and family.
